-- S. Africa Union to Campaign Against Wal-Mart’s Bid for Massmart
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2010-11-01T09:28:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-01/south-african-labor-union-to-campaign-against-wal-mart-s-bid-for-massmart.html
The South African Commercial,
Catering and Allied Workers’ Union said it will start a campaign
against Wal-Mart Stores Inc.’s plan to buy Massmart Holdings
Ltd.  The labor union will hold a press conference on Nov. 4 to
give details on the campaign, it said in a press statement
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  